3.text: A Time to Talk When a friend calls to me from the road
3.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>A Time to Talk When a friend calls to me from the road</prosody></speak>

4.text: and slows his horse to a meaning walk,
4.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>and slows his horse to a meaning walk,</prosody></speak>

5.text: I don't stand still and look around
5.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>I don't stand still and look around</prosody></speak>

6.text: on all the hills I haven't hoed, and shout from where I am, 'What is it?'
6.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>on all the hills I haven't hoed, and shout from where I am, 'What is it?'</prosody></speak>

7.text: No, not as there is a time to talk. I thrust my hoe in the mellow ground,
7.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>No, not as there is a time to talk. I thrust my hoe in the mellow ground,</prosody></speak>

8.text: blade-end up and five feet tall, and plod: I go up to the stone wall
